Package org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata

Class FabricContractInfo<TContractType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.ContractInfo<TContractType,FabricMethodInfo,FabricEventInfo>
      • org.blockchainnative.fabric.metadata.FabricContractInfo<TContractType>
  • public class FabricContractInfo<TContractType>
extends ContractInfo<TContractType,FabricMethodInfo,FabricEventInfo>
    Holds all relevant information about smart contract interfaces in order to allow FabricContractWrapperGenerator to generate a functioning wrapper class.

    It is recommended to use FabricContractInfoBuilder to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    FabricContractWrapperGenerator
